'''喜達屋酒店及度假村國際集團'''（{{lang-en|'''Starwood Hotels & Resorts Worldwide, Inc.'''}}）是世界最大的[[酒店|酒店]]集團之一，於1980年成立，1998年更名為現有名稱。集團總部設於[[美國|美國]][[紐約|紐約]]，旗下包括八個酒店主線品牌，在全球皆有直營據點與品牌授權經營，共95個國家擁有超過1500間酒店及度假村。

2015年10月28日'''喜達屋酒店及度假酒店國際集團'''以13億美元出售旗下[[分時度假|分時度假]]業務公司Vistana Signature Experiences給邁阿密分時度假集團（Interval Leisure Group）

2016年3月12日[[萬豪國際|萬豪國際]]以每股21美元現金，外加0.8股的萬豪國際普通股，折合每股79.53美元，斥資136億美元收購'''喜達屋酒店及度假酒店國際集團'''，創造全球最大的[[連鎖酒店|連鎖酒店]]。在获得美国监管机构许可后，合并于2016年9月23日完成。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/roadwarriorvoices/2016/09/23/marriott-starwood-merger-complete-and-loyal-customers-get-reciprocal-benefits/90885318/|last=Trejos|first=Nancy|title=Marriott, Starwood merger is complete, loyalty programs will reciprocate|work=USA Today|date=September 23, 2016|accessdate=September 24, 2016|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804134302/https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/roadwarriorvoices/2016/09/23/marriott-starwood-merger-complete-and-loyal-customers-get-reciprocal-benefits/90885318/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此之后，喜达屋SPG俱乐部与万豪礼赏开始进行会籍匹配。这两个[[忠诚计划|忠诚计划]]将于2018年8月18日合并。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/roadwarriorvoices/2016/09/23/marriott-starwood-merger-complete-and-loyal-customers-get-reciprocal-benefits/90885318/|title=Marriott, Starwood merger is complete, loyalty programs will reciprocate|website=USA Today|accessdate=24 September 2016|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804134302/https://www.usatoday.com/story/travel/roadwarriorvoices/2016/09/23/marriott-starwood-merger-complete-and-loyal-customers-get-reciprocal-benefits/90885318/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2018-08-01/the-marriott-starwood-merger-puts-a-points-program-to-the-test|title=Points-Obsessed Travelers Are Terrified of Losing Perks|work=Bloomberg.com|access-date=2018-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803083808/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2018-08-01/the-marriott-starwood-merger-puts-a-points-program-to-the-test|archive-date=2018-08-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年11月30日，万豪国际发布消息称，喜达屋酒店的客户预订数据库遭到了入侵，预计有5亿客户的个人信息被黑客盗取。经调查发现，自2014年起就有黑客非法访问了数据库。受此影响，万豪国际的股价在当天下午[[收盘|收盘]]时暴跌了5.59%。随后，美国和英国的监管部门分别对此事展开了调查。<ref>{{cite web |title=万豪酒店多达5亿客人详细信息或遭泄露 |url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/2668269.html |website=界面新闻 |accessdate=2019-01-08 |date=2018-11-30 |archive-date=2021-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104232926/https://www.jiemian.com/article/2668269.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=万豪旗下喜达屋预定系统被黑 5亿客人信息或泄露 |url=http://news.haiwainet.cn/n/2018/1130/c3541093-31449725.html |website=人民日报海外网 |accessdate=2019-01-08 |date=2018-11-30 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820210827/http://news.haiwainet.cn/n/2018/1130/c3541093-31449725.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=旗下喜达屋酒店数据库遭入侵 万豪股价暴跌5.59% |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2018/1202/c1002-30436631.html |website=人民网国际频道 |accessdate=2019-01-08 |date=2018-12-02 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820204741/http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2018/1202/c1002-30436631.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=万豪国际证实数据库遭黑客攻击 下调受影响客户数量 |url=https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2019/01-07/8721629.shtml |website=中国新闻网 |accessdate=2019-01-08 |date=2019-01-07 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105030802/https://www.chinanews.com/gj/2019/01-07/8721629.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>路透社引述消息人士称，中国的情报机构可能参与了这项网络入侵行动。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Christopher Bing |title=Exclusive: Clues in Marriott hack implicate China |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-marriott-intnl-cyber-china-exclusive/exclusive-clues-in-marriott-hack-implicate-china-sources-idUSKBN1O504D |website=Reuters |accessdate=2019-01-08 |language=en |date=2018-12-06 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211010004/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-marriott-intnl-cyber-china-exclusive/exclusive-clues-in-marriott-hack-implicate-china-sources-idUSKBN1O504D |dead-u